      "Step 3 — Close your eyes and have a friend place a specimen in your hand. Try to identify it by feel. Practice until you can name at least five of eight by touch alone.",
      "Step 4 — Arrange your egg-carton display: label each compartment with the specimen name and its type. Practice explaining one specimen's story to a friend in two sentences.",
