      "Step 3 — Add the final five paintings. Now shuffle all fifteen and test yourself. Set aside any you miss and spend extra time with those — look at the details that make each one unique.",
      "Step 4 — Quiz with a partner: show each other the painting and race to name it. Practice until you can name all fifteen in under two minutes total.",
