    "pass_criteria": "Correctly identify 15 of 15 famous paintings by both title and artist, in random order, without prompting.",
    "counselor_notes": "Monet/Manet confusion is almost guaranteed — include both and make the kid distinguish them. Ensure the fifteen include works from at least three continents."
