      "Step 2 — Add five more countries (e.g., India, Kenya, Mexico, Norway, Thailand). Same process: find, color, label. Quiz yourself on all ten using a fresh blank map — point to the country and name the capital.",
      "Step 3 — Add the final five countries (e.g., South Korea, Argentina, Canada, South Africa, Turkey). Now you have fifteen. Use your third blank map for a full self-test.",
