    "pass_criteria": "On a blank world map, correctly locate 15 of 15 countries and name all 15 capitals without any errors.",
    "counselor_notes": "The 'trick' capitals (Canberra, Brasília, Ankara, Naypyidaw) are where most kids fail — make sure at least three are in the fifteen."
